{"tid":1286822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有感而發) 強國管治威信非一般的高","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T03:34:54.000Z","uid":217285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"30f8eea5914d281da6182c848d322813702b8305","tid":1286822,"uid":217285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"人在海外<br />\n工作地方同學校都會有好多強國人<br />\n之前上media堂<br />\n老師講起新聞自由 天安門事件<br />\n有強國同學即刻起曬鋼<br />\n叫老師唔好亂講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我聽到已經好驚訝<br />\n強國人果然好愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到之後非洲豬瘟係強國爆發<br />\n近期武漢事件<br />\n強國人乜都唔知<br />\n國內消息被封鎖我可以理解<br />\n但連呢邊海外既華人媒體都隻字不提<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家鄉發生咩事都唔知<br />\n講咩愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係井底之蛙<br />\n經濟好左 又點？<br />\n分多啲錢比你？<br />\n強國人即使出左國<br />\n都仍然幫黨幫國講說話<br />\n成班籠中鳥<br />\n睇清楚事實啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔想香港以後變成咁<br />\n諗起強國式生活都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住大家<br />\n我唔係香港同大家一齊抗爭<br />\n我只可以幫手做下宣傳<br />\n香港人加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZXDUi0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZXDUi0C.jpg&h=6d56964d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdzL97k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdzL97k.png&h=9aa9849d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}